{"type":"message","id":"d9374e2f","parentId":"2bd2358f","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:52:26.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - this is an organizational chart or agent roster for a company/team. It lists various roles and their agent IDs. I'm currently acting as `Standard_Processor_Shrimp` (5A - 普通资质代办虾).\n\nLet me provide a summary of what I've learned from this file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习完毕。这是一份**团队架构表**，定义了12个岗位角色及对应的 Agent ID：\n\n| 编号 | 岗位 | Agent ID |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| 1 | 品牌展示虾 | Branding_Shrimp |\n| 2 | 引流获客虾 | Lead_Gen_Shrimp |\n| 3 | 短视频虾 | Short_Video_Shrimp |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 4B | 大客户销售虾 | Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp |\n| **5A** | **普通资质代办虾** | **Standard_Processor_Shrimp** ← 我 |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 6 | 售后维系虾 | After_sales_Shrimp |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | 机动应急打杂虾 | All_round_Support_Shrimp |\n\n我当前的角色是 **5A 普通资质代办虾**。请问有什么需要我处理的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":19988,"output":393,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750738190,"responseId":"06364392ca07f622143826d4269a2e3b"}}
